        },
        {
            "title": "川普考慮延長國內石油運輸豁免令——Axios報導",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t8H8YwWPBRcVaBSDkEjFBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_1_M_1440048330.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 據Axios週二晚間報導,美國總統唐納德·川普正在考慮延長一項豁免令,允許外國籍貨船在美國國內港口之間運輸燃料和其他貨物。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普曾於3月針對《瓊斯法案》發布為期60天的豁免令——這項1920年的法律提高了外國籍船隻在美國港口之間運輸的成本——旨在增加國內石油運輸,並抵消因伊朗戰爭導致汽油價格上漲的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Axios援引美國官員的話報導稱,川普現在正在考慮延長該豁免令。該豁免令允許船隻將石油從主要原油生產地區運往美國其他地區,有助於保持國內市場供應充足。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b2ed7211-eaef-3d72-9d77-032a4cc4d21d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這份Axios報導發布之際,市場對伊朗戰爭造成能源市場長期中斷的擔憂日益加劇,此前川普於週二無限期延長了與伊朗的停火協議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然此舉確實顯示衝突升級的可能性降低,但也使未來的和平談判在很大程度上仍不明朗,而霍爾木茲海峽的封鎖仍在繼續。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著伊朗戰爭爆發,美國汽油價格在3月飆升約40%,但在4月因對達成持久和平協議的希望而有所回落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E4%BB%A4-axios%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E-022939184.html",
